item.title: Feedback for some new songs I would love to post!
item.dc:creator: Tropical_Madman
item.description:
Hey! I edited the “We Are Warriors” track. I love the melody and the way it was put together!

It did need some editing and more tone variation. I made little few changes and added labels of what’s mine and what I didn’t change. Should say something like “WJ EDIT” or “Winter J. Edit”. I also added labels for the scene for what parts I left alone too. Hopefully this makes it sound better.

Link: We Are Warriors Edit

I’m also listening to the other tracks and they are also really awesome.

Edit note: I also forgot to mention that in my opinion the piano sounds a little to loud or overpowering the some of the sounds. So far everything else sounds great! Turning down the Lowpass should make the piano sound more “lively”.
